216
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,460
To...

217
00:20:36,900 --> 00:20:38,500
Ten strom má démona?

218
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,260
Démon?

219
00:20:39,460 --> 00:20:41,360
Prečo... Musíme odísť!

220
00:20:42,960 --> 00:20:44,480
Nemôžete odo mňa odísť!

221
00:20:44,580 --> 00:20:45,720
Kto to povedal?

