00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:46,900
Kto?

223
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:48,600
Kto?

224
00:20:49,020 --> 00:20:54,180
Ublížili ste mojim príbuzným
a teraz chcete odísť? Snívate!

225
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:55,220
Dnes...

226
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:58,400
vás tu všetkých zabijem!

227
00:20:58,460 --> 00:20:58,940
Kto?

228
00:21:00,220 --> 00:21:00,520
Kto?

229
00:21:06,420 --> 00:21:08,700
Bežme! Zachráňme si životy!

230
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,320
Dosť!

231
00:21:23,460 --> 00:21:26,540
Ukáž sa! Je to moja vina!

232
00:21:44,660 --> 00:21:45,760
Zheng! Poďme!

