00:22:07,820 --> 00:22:09,260
Nechoď sem! Uteč!

240
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:10,120
Yu Yan!

241
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:11,780
Zheng! Rýchlo uteč!

242
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:15,340
