249
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:04,560
Ale teraz...

250
00:23:04,940 --> 00:23:06,700
som ťa uzdravila.

251
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:09,720
Prosím, nechaj ho ísť!

252
00:23:23,420 --> 00:23:23,980
Zheng!

